<p>The refresh color doesn't match the tint color and looks different, i tryied to change tintAdjustmentMode but the result is the same</p>  <p>Just to note, the spinner and text color should be 0x2C76BE </p>  <pre><code>tvc.refreshControl = [UIRefreshControl new]; tvc.refreshControl.tintAdjustmentMode = UIViewTintAdjustmentModeNormal; tvc.refreshControl.tintColor = [UIColor colorWithHex:0x2C76BE]; tvc.refreshControl.attributedTitle = [[NSAttributedString alloc] initWithString:@"Pull to query spectrum again" attributes:@{NSForegroundColorAttributeName:[UIColor colorWithHex:0x2C76BE]}]; </code></pre>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/yiT9k.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/yiT9k.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>